## Review Sidecar Template

The `.review-needed.md` file MUST follow this structure. This is an **offline review artifact** — the pipeline does NOT stop here. Domain experts review it at their own pace, and corrections trigger a selective review-rerun (Phase 11 + ALTER re-deploy only).

```markdown
